# Документация

Порядок изменений: **OpenSpec change → архитектура → код → archive**.

- Поведение (канон): `openspec/specs/<capability>/spec.md`
- Изменения: `openspec/changes/<id>/` (proposal, tasks, delta specs)
- Бизнес: [docs/requirements/business/](docs/requirements/business/)
- ADR: [docs/architecture/adr/template.md](docs/architecture/adr/template.md)
- REST-контракт: [docs/architecture/openapi/components/openapi.yaml](docs/architecture/openapi/components/openapi.yaml)
- C4: LikeC4 в `docs/architecture/diagram/` + [docs/ai/context/containers.md](docs/ai/context/containers.md)
- SPDF: [docs/FRAMEWORK.md](docs/FRAMEWORK.md), [docs/manifest.yaml](docs/manifest.yaml)
- Не противоречь принятым ADR без нового ADR
